OL,7,FA fugitive mother and father, whose
OL,8,Fbaby died after they went off-grid in
OL,9,FSussex have been found guilty of
OL,10,Fconcealing the birth of a child and
OL,11,Fperverting the course of justice, it
OL,12,Fcan now be reported.
OL,14,FA jury at the Old Bailey has heard how
OL,15,Fwealthy aristocrat Constance Marten,
OL,16,F37, and her partner Mark Gordon, 49,
OL,17,Ffled authorities in January 2023 in an
OL,18,Fattempt to keep their newborn child
OL,19,Fafter four other children were taken
OL,20,Finto care.
