OL,4,Cbirth after baby found in bag inside
OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FThe pair were arrested in Brighton on
OL,8,F27 February 2023, two days before
OL,9,Ftheir daughter Victoria's decomposed
OL,10,Fbody was found inside a Lidl bag in a
OL,11,Fdisused allotment shed.
OL,13,FThe cause of the child's death could
OL,14,Fnot be established.
OL,16,FThe jury found the couple guilty of
OL,17,Fconcealing the birth of a child and
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice.
