OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FThe couple had also faced charges of
OL,8,Fchild cruelty, manslaughter by gross
OL,9,Fnegligence and causing or allowing the
OL,10,Fdeath of a child, all of which they
OL,11,Fdenied.
OL,13,FThe trial at the Old Bailey began on
OL,14,FJanuary 25. Jurors began deliberating
OL,15,Fon April 30 and were discharged after
OL,16,Fmore than 72 hours of deliberation.
OL,18,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC gave his
OL,19,F"sincere and heartfelt thanks" to
OL,20,Fjurors for their "truly exceptional"
OL,21,Fdedication.
