OL,7,F"Please do not feel that you have
OL,8,Ffailed in any way," he said.
OL,10,FThe judge gave them the option of
OL,11,Flifetime exemption from jury service.
OL,13,FOn Wednesday, prosecutor Tom Little KC
OL,14,Fannounced the Crown would seek a
OL,15,Fretrial as Judge Mark Lucraft KC
OL,16,Fallowed reporting of the two verdicts
OL,17,Ffollowing an application by PA news
OL,18,Fagency.
