OL,7,FJudge Lucraft set a provisional six to
OL,8,Feight-week retrial from March 3 next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FJurors heard that police began a
OL,12,Fsearch for the missing baby after a
OL,13,Fplacenta was found in a burning car on
OL,14,Fthe motorway near Bolton, Greater
OL,15,FManchester, last January 5.
OL,17,FThe defendants had fled the scene with
OL,18,FVictoria under Marten's jacket,
OL,19,Fleaving behind a cat in a box, about
OL,20,F#2,000 in cash, 34 "burner" phones and
OL,21,Fother belongings, the trial heard.
