OL,7,FThey travelled by taxis from the North
OL,8,FWest to Harwich in Essex, East Ham in
OL,9,FLondon and on to Newhaven, East Sussex.
OL,11,FVictoria was briefly glimpsed on CCTV
OL,12,Ffootage in London wearing a teddy bear
OL,13,Fmotif babygrow.
OL,15,FPolice body-worn camera footage
OL,16,Fcaptured the moment the defendants
OL,17,Fwere arrested after buying supplies in
OL,18,FBrighton last February 27.
